Metadata.Title: Dartmoor Blackout
Metadata.Description: Good afternoon, 47, welcome to Dartmoor.Our client is a contestant of Dartmoor Garden Show, who noticed that contestant Ken Takeuchi colluded with judge Sebastian Sato and several employees, tring to eliminate other competitors and opposing judges, to make that himself win.So ... zi ... the client decided to ... zi ... answer blows with blows ... zi zi ... assassinate them ... zi ... Your targets include ... zi zi ... Never gonna give you up  ... zi ... never gonna let you down ... zi zi ...
